<p>The difference between AI content that ranks and AI content that sits on page 5 is the prompt. <a href="https://searchengineland.com/guide/seo-prompts-for-chatgpt">86% of SEO professionals use AI tools</a> like ChatGPT for content creation. But most use vague prompts that produce vague content.</p>
